{"tid":2513343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(死亡之吻) 新加坡疫情再反彈 新增39宗確診","createTime":"2021-05-02T12:25:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T16:37:58.000Z","uid":112747,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7273be9f7a4c85e72d795c58ae9f4a36f50e1940","tid":2513343,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T12:25:16.000Z","msg":"月底將與本港實施「旅遊氣泡」的新加坡疫情反彈，單日新增39宗新冠確診病例，政府收緊防疫措施及禁止曾到南亞多國的旅客入境，並呼籲民眾每日不要參與多於兩場社交活動。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡的新冠疫情升溫，星期日新增39人確診，其中14人是社區感染，大部分與一間醫院的感染群組有關。而當地過去一周社區感染個案有35宗，遠高於再前一周的10宗，而且出現多宗源頭不明個案。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡政府也宣布，禁止在過去兩周內曾前往孟加拉、尼泊爾、巴基斯坦和斯里蘭卡的旅客入境。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡與香港計劃在本月26日啟動「旅遊氣泡」，根據兩地協議，如果任何一方源頭不明個案的七天平均數超過5宗，「旅遊氣泡」就要暫停兩周。"},{"pid":"ede28455c96a6d96dfc3572df91c427f1c4588ea","tid":2513343,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T12:25:31.000Z","msg":"monkey see monkey do"},{"pid":"e68f0196e3ab1b4e32c0da2b17cd788eaa775a65","tid":2513343,"uid":14941,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T12:26:39.000Z","msg":"香港帶過去果個堅呀<br />\n瘋狂傳播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01353e1949fdbc17e28e4055b2d4501e4f636702","tid":2513343,"uid":241804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:30:10.000Z","msg":"如果任何一方源頭不明個案的七天平均數超過5宗，「旅遊氣泡」就要暫停兩周。<br />\n<br />\n唔知仲有幾多quota呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3dc866443b881618012c3a55b5d217fb6f13c3","tid":2513343,"uid":8810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"01353e1949fdbc17e28e4055b2d4501e4f636702","tid":2513343,"uid":241804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,